Duk-su, you want to ride that?

547
00:44:02,120 --> 00:44:03,120
Yeah!

548
00:44:03,120 --> 00:44:05,240
Giddy-up, giddy-up!

549
00:44:08,360 --> 00:44:10,480
Alright, I'll let you go for a ride.

550
00:44:10,480 --> 00:44:12,720
Yay! How exciting!

551
00:44:18,320 --> 00:44:21,040
Twinkle, twinkle??

