00:44:21,040 --> 00:44:23,560
?å¥¹n the Eastern sky??

553
00:44:27,240 --> 00:44:28,640
Sister!

554
00:44:29,160 --> 00:44:30,520
Duk-su??

555
00:44:35,680 --> 00:44:37,280
Duk-su??

556
00:44:43,160 --> 00:44:44,240
Mom??

557
