Duk-mi's a strong girl, so I'm sure she'll be fine.

564
00:45:46,440 --> 00:45:47,560
Duk-mi.

565
00:45:50,360 --> 00:45:53,640
Mom, I'm sorry.

566
00:45:53,640 --> 00:45:55,400
I'm really sorry, Mom.

567
